      "content": "Hey, I'm a nurse in the ER and I need some help prioritizing these intakes. I've got two people coming in at the same time.\n\nPatient 1: A 45-year-old Caucasian male, dressed in professional business attire. He is complaining of sudden, heavy chest pressure and shortness of breath. He appears visibly pale and is sweating heavily.\n\nCan you give me some diagnostic considerations and a triage priority for him?",
